<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/women-and-equalities-unit/about> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Women and Equalities Unit is part of the Office for Equality and Opportunity. We lead work on policy relating to gender equality, LGBT+ people and the overall framework of equality legislation in the UK."@en .
